casebody.data:
Feichtner, Admr., Appellant, v. Ohio Department of Transportation, Appellee.

[Cite as Feichtner v. Ohio Dept. of Transp. (1997), 78 Ohio St.3d 1207.]

(No. 95-2279 Submitted March 5, 1997 Decided April 9, 1997.) Joseph L. Coticchia, for appellant. Betty D. Montgomery, Attorney General, and Velda K. Hofacker, Assistant Attorney General, for appellee.

The appeal is dismissed, sua sponte, as having been improvidently allowed.

Moyer, C.J., Douglas, Resnick, F.E. Sweeney, Pfeifer, Cook and Lundberg Stratton, JJ., concur.
